        <li><strong>Multi-head attention:</strong> Captures diverse relationships simultaneously</li>
        <li><strong>Positional encoding:</strong> Injects sequence order information</li>
        <li><strong>Residual connections + LayerNorm:</strong> Supports training deeper networks</li>
